replies.body:
No summoner spell should have a huge impact on the game?

{{summoner:4}}
Make plays, initiate, escape.

{{summoner:14}}
Increase damage output and secure kills, completely cripples healing champions.

{{summoner:11}}
Controls baron and dragon, can decide the game.

{{summoner:12}} 
Grants massive global map pressure, can turn teamfights, save towers/allies, or contest objectives.
